印度的'''[[鬥雞|鬥雞]]'''（{{lang-te|Kodi Pandem}}；{{lang-ta|Vetrukkaal seval porr}}；{{lang-ml|kozhi kettu}}）習俗主要發生在每年的1月，恰逢{{tsl|en|Makar Sankranti|瑪克桑格拉提節}}。儘管該習俗在印度為非法行為，但在[[安德拉邦|安德拉邦]]的沿海地區仍普遍盛行，包括[[克利須那縣|克利須那縣]]、[[貢土爾縣|貢土爾縣]]、[[東哥達瓦里縣|東哥達瓦里縣]]和[[西哥達瓦里縣|西哥達瓦里縣]]。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/the-roosters-wear-razors-inside-indias-super-bowl-of-cockfighting/2019/02/04/63476888-1e60-11e9-a759-2b8541bbbe20_story.html |title=Inside India’s illegal ‘Super Bowl’ of cockfighting, where the roosters wear razors |last=Slater |first=Joanna |date=2019-02-05 |newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |accessdate=2020-10-15 |language=en-US |issn=0190-8286 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028163949/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/the-roosters-wear-razors-inside-indias-super-bowl-of-cockfighting/2019/02/04/63476888-1e60-11e9-a759-2b8541bbbe20_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite news|last=Srinivas|first=Rajulapudi|date=2020-01-12|title=Despite ban, stage being set for cockfighting in Andhra Pradesh|language=en|work=[[印度報|The Hindu]]|url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/fowl-play/article30546425.ece|access-date=2020-08-22|issn=0971-751X|archive-date=2020-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200112151952/https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/fowl-play/article30546425.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 概述 ==
[[File:Battle_of_Palnadu_sculpture_in_Telugu_Museum.jpg|thumb]]
據說自[[印度歷史|古印度]]就有安排[[原雞屬|原雞]]和[[公雞|公雞]]互相打鬥的娛樂活動。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web |title=Bird Fights |url=http://www.bwcindia.org/Web/Awareness/LearnAbout/BirdFights.html |language=en |access-date=2020-08-24 |website=Beauty Without Cruelty - India |archive-date=2022-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220327150804/http://bwcindia.org/Web/Awareness/LearnAbout/BirdFights.html }}</ref>根據紀載，{{tsl|en|Battle of Palnadu|帕爾納杜戰役}}（1178－1182年）的結果即是由公雞爭鬥決定，此後鬥雞文化得以在[[安德拉邦|安德拉邦]]立足。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/a-favourite-pastime/article30546348.ece |title=A favourite pastime |last=Bhattacharjee |first=Sumit |date=2020-01-12 |work=The Hindu |language=en |issn=0971-751X |access-date=2020-08-25 |archive-date=2020-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019000702/https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/a-favourite-pastime/article30546348.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>鬥雞活動現今在安德拉邦和印度的其他地區均有舉行，包括[[卡納塔克邦|卡納塔克邦]]、[[坦米爾納杜邦|坦米爾納杜邦]]、[[喀拉拉邦|喀拉拉邦]]和[[奧里薩邦|奧里薩邦]]等。<ref name=":1" />

當地有專門為鬥雞而飼養的公雞，其腳上綁有刀和刀片，且在通常在打鬥的過程中會造成其中一隻公雞死亡。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Bommakanti|first=Ujwal|last2=|last3=|first3=|date=2020-01-15|title=Cockfights continue across Andhra Pradesh despite court ban {{!}} Vijayawada News - Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/vijayawada/cockfight-arenas-spring-up-lakhs-trade-hands-as-organisers-flout-ban/articleshow/73257193.cms|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411224720/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/vijayawada/cockfight-arenas-spring-up-lakhs-trade-hands-as-organisers-flout-ban/articleshow/73257193.cms|archive-date=2021-04-11|access-date=2020-08-22|website=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]]|language=en}}</ref>公雞長期接受鬥雞訓練，身價可達50,000[[印度盧比|印度盧比]]。在{{tsl|en|Makar Sankranti|瑪克桑格拉提節|瑪克桑格拉提}}風箏節期間，會組織一場為期三天的活動，每次吸引數千人參與。<ref name=":0" />美國《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》在2019年的一份調查中稱該活動為「鬥雞界的[[超级碗|超级碗]]」（Super Bowl of cockfighting）。<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|date=2020-01-22|title=Man killed by chicken at illegal cockfight|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/india-man-killed-rooster-cockfight-razor-blades-andhra-pradesh-a9296531.html|author=Adam Withnall|access-date=2020-08-22|location=Delhi|website=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102173056/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/india-man-killed-rooster-cockfight-razor-blades-andhra-pradesh-a9296531.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
鬥雞是一種古老的觀賞性運動。有證據顯示，鬥雞作為消遣活動存在於[[印度河流域文明|印度河流域文明]]中<ref name="Sherman">{{Cite book |title=Tending Animals in the Global Village |last=David M |first=Sherman |publisher=Blackwell Publishing |year=2002 |isbn=0-683-18051-7 |pages=46}}</ref>，2008年版《[[大英百科全書|大英百科全書]]》寫明：<ref>{{Cite web |title=Cockfighting |url=https://www.britannica.com/sports/cockfighting |accessdate=2021-03-03 |date=2008 |work=Encyclopedia Britannica |publisher=Encyclopædia Britannica |language=en |archive-date=2022-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516154031/https://www.britannica.com/sports/cockfighting }}</ref>
{{Quote|這項運動在古代盛行於印度、中國、波斯和其他東方國家，並於特米斯托克力時期（約西元前524－460年）傳入古希臘，後遍布小亞細亞及西西里。羅馬人有很長一段時間對這種「希臘式消遣」（Greek diversion）嗤之以鼻，但最終仍熱情地接納這種運動，以致農業作家科魯邁拉（西元1世紀）抱怨道，其讀者曾將他們所有的家產拿來下注街邊的賭博。}}

印度學者{{tsl|en|Iravatham Mahadevan|伊拉瓦瑟姆·馬哈德萬}}根據其對[[摩亨佐-達羅|摩亨佐-達羅]]圖章的分析，推測該城市的古名可能為「Kukkutarma」（直譯「公雞[kukkuta]的城市[-rma]」）。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Address' Signs of the Indus Script |url=http://www.thehindu.com/multimedia/archive/00151/Dr_Iravatham_Mahade_151204a.pdf |author={{tsl|en|Iravatham Mahadevan|伊拉瓦瑟姆·馬哈德萬|Iravatham Mahadevan}} |date=2010-06-23－27 |format=PDF |publisher=The Hindu |location={{tsl|en|World Classical Tamil Conference 2010|2010年世界古典泰米爾會議}} |access-date=2021-03-03 |archive-date=2011-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110110100458/http://www.thehindu.com/multimedia/archive/00151/Dr_Iravatham_Mahade_151204a.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=3DVVvgAACAAJ&dq=Poultry+Breeding+and+Genetics&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiFqPTcw5TvAhVlL6YKHY3cCBoQ6AEwAHoECAIQAg |title=Poultry Breeding and Genetics |author=R. D. Crawford |publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences |year=1990 |isbn=0444885579 |pages=10}}</ref>然而，一項研究顯示無法確認這些雞隻是否影響現代家禽的演化<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Al-Nasser|first1=A.|last2=Al-Khalaifa|first2=H.|last3=Al-Saffar|first3=A.|last4=Khalil|first4=F.|last5=Albahouh|first5=M.|last6=Ragheb|first6=G.|last7=Al-Haddad|first7=A.|last8=Mashaly|first8=M.|year=2007|title=Overview of chicken taxonomy and domestication|journal=World's Poultry Science Journal|volume=63|issue=2|pages=285|doi=10.1017/S004393390700147X<!---|s2cid=86734013--->}}</ref>，而來自印度河流域的[[哈拉帕_(巴基斯坦)|哈拉帕文明]]（西元前2500－2100年）的雞則可能是該鳥類遍佈世界各地的主要來源。印度河流域文明中，多個跡象表明當時的雞僅用於格鬥，而非作為食物食用<ref name="google11">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=3DVVvgAACAAJ&dq=Poultry+Breeding+and+Genetics&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiFqPTcw5TvAhVlL6YKHY3cCBoQ6AEwAHoECAIQAg |title=Poultry Breeding and Genetics |author=R. D. Crawford |work=Developments in animal and veterinary sciences |publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences |year=1990 |isbn=0444885579 |pages=10}}</ref>，且雞直至西元前1000年時已具有「宗教意義」。<ref name="google11" />

== Kukkuta Sastra ==
《Kukkuta Satra》（直譯''公雞占星術''）是一部論述鬥雞的{{tsl|en|Shastra|聖典}}，該書未記載作者或成書時間等訊息<ref name=":4">{{Cite news|title=కోడిపందేల చరిత్ర తెలిసి ఉండొచ్చు.. మరి కోడి చరిత్ర తెలుసా?|language=te|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] తెలుగు|url=https://www.bbc.com/telugu/india-42652250|access-date=2020-08-19|date=2018-01-12|archive-date=2020-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017180411/https://www.bbc.com/telugu/india-42652250|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，其認可了50種適合鬥雞的公雞，亦規範了公雞的飼料，包括但不限於[[扁桃|扁桃]]、[[腰果|腰果]]、[[開心果|開心果]]和肉。在印度飼養的鬥雞也須嚴格遵守《Kukkuta Satra》。<ref name="nt">{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2016-01-10|title=కాలుదువ్వుతున్న పందెంకోళ్లు... {{!}} ఖమ్మం|url=http://m.navatelangana.com/article/khammam/193083|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413215004/http://m.navatelangana.com/article/khammam/193083|archive-date=2021-04-13|access-date=2020-08-19|website={{tsl|en|Nava Telangana|納瓦特蘭伽納報|Nava Telangana}}|language=te}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last1=K|first1=Srinivas|date=2011-01-12|title=కోట్ల రూపాయల కోడి పందేలు|url=http://www.suryaa.com/features/article-1-12718|archive-url=https://archive.today/20140113135722/http://www.suryaa.com/features/article-1-12718|archive-date=2014-01-13|accessdate=2014-01-13|website={{tsl|en|Suryaa (newspaper)|Suryaa (報紙)|Suryaa}}|language=te|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 禁止 ==
自1960年頒布《{{tsl|en|Prevention of Cruelty to Animals Act|防止虐待動物法}}》以來，鬥雞在印度境內已被視為非法行為，且隨後在2015年[[印度最高法院|印度最高法院]]和2016年{{tsl|en|Telangana High Court|泰倫加納高等法院|海得拉巴土高等法院}}（今泰倫加納高等法院）的判決維持這一禁令。<ref>{{Cite web|author=Esha Mitra|title=Man dies after rooster attack on way to cockfight|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/01/22/india/rooster-cockfight-death-intl-hnk-scli/index.html|access-date=2020-08-22|date=2020-01-23|location=New Delhi|website=[[CNN|CNN]]|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126152337/https://www.cnn.com/2020/01/22/india/rooster-cockfight-death-intl-hnk-scli/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2017-01-12|title=Despite Ban, Roosters and Punters Ready for the Cockfights|url=https://www.news18.com/news/india/despite-ban-roosters-and-punters-ready-for-the-cockfights-1334749.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017022731/https://www.news18.com/news/india/despite-ban-roosters-and-punters-ready-for-the-cockfights-1334749.html|archive-date=2020-10-17|access-date=2020-08-22|website=[[CNN-News18|News18]]|author=Sakshi Khanna|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年1月，最高法院允許以不使用刀或刀片的傳統方式舉行該項活動，同時禁止[[賭博|賭博]]或下注。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2018-01-13|author=Srinivasa Rao Apparasu|location=Hyderabad|title=SC allows conduct of cockfights in 'traditional manner' in coastal Andhra|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/sc-allows-conduct-of-cockfights-in-traditional-manner-in-coastal-andhra/story-Iqy4q3u2WIlismJeP0OFSP.html|access-date=2020-08-22|website=[[印度斯坦時報|The Hindustan Times]]|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016231032/https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/sc-allows-conduct-of-cockfights-in-traditional-manner-in-coastal-andhra/story-Iqy4q3u2WIlismJeP0OFSP.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

儘管受到法令限制<ref name=":3" />，鬥雞活動依然盛行於安德拉邦，2019年的三天活動中的賭注金額估計達900[[克若|克若]]印度盧比，該邦有超過20萬隻公雞被用於鬥雞。<ref name=":5">{{Cite web|title=cockfights: Cockfights have turned into a multi-crore biz in coastal Andhra Pradesh|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/sunday-times/cockfights-have-turned-into-a-multi-crore-biz-in-coastal-andhra-pradesh/articleshow/67599224.cms|author=Syed Akbar|date=2019-01-19|access-date=2020-08-22|website=The Times of India|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107232437/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/sunday-times/cockfights-have-turned-into-a-multi-crore-biz-in-coastal-andhra-pradesh/articleshow/67599224.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>

